summary:
Ever entered the Dawnstar sanctuary and said to yourself, I paid 19000 gold for this, well, this aims to fix that, one step at a time
*SPOILERS*
descriptionHtml:
This is basically an overhaul of the dawnstar sanctuary, its starting off small, but I hope it gets bigger, currently all we have is
1.New doors to main city of each hold(excluding dawnstar of course)
Future plans I have are
1.Re work the master bedroom(likely coming soon)
2.Add more assassins(mid range wait)
3.Make it so that delvin takes the letter of credit for 15000 gold, and only charges you 2000 gold for repairs(At some point I hope)
4. add new purchasable upgrades(I woefully doubt I can do this, any help would be appreciated)
author: Ryuzaki1
